***Title VIII, Section 801 of the Energy Policy Act of 1992 directed the National Academy of Sciences to determine "whether it is possible to make scientifically supportable predictions of the probability that the repository's engineered or geologic barriers will be breached as a result of human intrusion over a period of 10,000 years."
